ygData.messageBody:
There was a map that was posted to http://www.majestic-worlds.com/runnyeye/
that was listed on stratics about a week ago. I just tried the link and it
was giving me a 403 error so it may be that the link has been restricted.
It had a detailed map of the entire runnyeye zone that was far more detailed
than any other map I'd seen. The place is huge. If you really want to see
it and you can't get the link to work, send me a private email and I'll see
if I can find it in my temp files.

-----Original Message-----
From: Philip Jon Terry [mailto:pjt006@...]
Sent: Monday, October 18, 1999 4:15 PM
To: EQ_Tinkering@onelist.com
Subject: [EQ_Tinkering] Water Tunnel


From: "Philip Jon Terry" <pjt006@...>

Runny Eye. Broxx the Evil Eye with the Observor Staff spawns here. But
there is also a seemingly massive canal system (I heard four levels deep)
that I saw with a waterfall flowing down into it. I dropped onto the bridge
but had to gate out when a slime elemental ran into me. Has anyone explored
the water in this zone? What is down there?

Spring, 18th Magician
Veeshan
